                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1010" type="given" value="ALFRED"></interp>ALFRED STANIFORD</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I have no servant—my wife has a sister, but she never had a word with the prisoner—my window was shut at night, and it was open in the morning, when I found him.</p>
